Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "Kamala Harris surrendered our energy independence -- She's vowed repeatedly to ban fracking... Then she said 'I'm in favor of fracking' -- The people of Pennsylvania are smart. They will not fall for it. If you do not have fracking, you do not have a commonwealth."
